OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry morning with
OL,6,Fpatchy cloud and long sunny spells.
OL,7,FThrough the afternoon cloud will
OL,8,Fspread northeastwards limiting any
OL,9,Fsunny spells with outbreaks of rain
OL,10,Fover Orkney by late afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with light
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain for Orkney, Shetland
OL,14,Fstaying dry. Remaining cloudy
OL,15,Fovernight with rain becoming heavier
OL,16,Fand more persistent for Orkney, some
OL,17,Flight rain for Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
