OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FBreezy, cloudy and dull with
OL,6,Fheavy and persistent rain over Orkney.
OL,7,FCloudy for Shetland with lighter,
OL,8,Fpatchier rain and a few brighter
OL,9,Fintervals.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,12,Fmixed few days which will be mostly
OL,13,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain at times
OL,14,Fbut still some dry and bright or sunny
OL,15,Fspells. Winds mostly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
